# Getting Started

This guide walks you through installing and configuring the Acme Design System in your project.

## Installation

```bash
npm install @acme/design-system
```

## Setup

Wrap your app in the `ThemeProvider` to enable design tokens:

```tsx
import { ThemeProvider } from '@acme/design-system';

function App() {
  return (
    <ThemeProvider>
      {/* your app */}
    </ThemeProvider>
  );
}
```

## Importing components

```tsx
import { Button, Alert } from '@acme/design-system';
```
